                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6625" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0319</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9210 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">芳华待灼，砥砺深耕——延长石油90后新生代员工融入之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Struggle in Youth——The Integration of New Generation of Post-90s Employees in Yanchang Oil Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋晓荣，秦婧怡，白建伟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西延长石油集团有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石油工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">延长石油；新生代员工；组织社会化；融入；适应；2022百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yanchang Oil Company; New Generation Employees; Organization Socialization; Integration; Adaptation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">90后新生代员工正在逐渐成为职场主力军，留住新生代员工对组织保持其核心竞争力具有重要意义。本案例以“进入阶段→适应阶段→融入阶段”的逻辑主线展开，描述了延长石油90后新生代员工的组织社会化过程，展示了延长石油从组织社会化的进入阶段到适应阶段、再到融入阶段，采取的针对新生代员工特点的各类社会化措施，帮助员工从自然人转变成“延长人”，并以国有企业“坚持党的领导毫不动摇”核心理念、基本的制度和秩序遵守作为组织社会化的重要内容，最终使新生代员工明晰发展路径、坚定理想信念、掌握工作技能、实现角色清晰和社会融合，从而成功融入延长石油。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The new generation of employees born after the 1990s are gradually becoming the main force in the workplace and retaining the new generation of employees is of great significance for the organization to maintain its core competitiveness. This case is developed with the logical main line of &quot;Entering the stage-Adaptation stage-Integration stage&quot;. Then describes the organizational socialization process of the new generation of post-90s employees of Yanchang oil company and shows that the Yanchang oil company from organization socialization into the stage to adaptation stage, to integration stage, various socialization measures for the characteristics of the new generation employees. Yanchang oil company help employees from natural person into &quot;Yanchang person&quot;, at the same time, with state-owned enterprises &quot;adhere to the leadership of the party&quot; unswervingly the core concept, the basic system and order as an important content of organization socialization. Eventually they make the new generation employees clear development path, firm ideal faith, master work skills, achieve clear role and social integration, thus successfully integrate into the Yanchang oil company.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《人力资源管理》、《管理学原理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">缺</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
